Seq1.CallerContent: Hi, this is Carol Heavey, and I'm coming in at 11.30 for my appointment today. But I got a call from the office this morning, and I didn't know what the call was.
Seq1.ReceiverContent: Good morning, this is Carl from Family Practice. How may I assist you today?

Seq2.CallerContent: Okay, well, my question is, they said they were scheduling. They told me to see a nurse practitioner, and I had a call last week about this, on Friday.
Seq2.ReceiverContent: May I know your last name, please?

Seq3.ReceiverContent: One moment, let me check on it. Yes, correct. So, your first name is Carol, am I correct?

Seq4.CallerContent: Well, they already contacted me with that information. That's why they said, would you rather have a call? And I guess, if I can't get the nurse practitioner, I guess I'll just get a call then.
Seq4.ReceiverContent: So, I'm really sorry to say this. Ma'am, Dr. Williamson is not feeling well today, so she needs to make it as a televisit. Would you like to make it as a televisit, or would you like to reschedule it?

Seq5.CallerContent: Oh, okay. All right. Well, then, if that's all I can have, I guess that's what I'll do.
Seq5.ReceiverContent: Yes, correct. You cannot get the nurse practitioner today. I'm sorry to say this. Would you like to change it as a televisit?

Seq6.CallerContent: Okay, well, okay. We'll do the phone thing.
Seq6.ReceiverContent: At the same time, on the same day, today, at the same time.

Seq7.CallerContent: Okay, honey. All right. Thank you so much.
Seq7.ReceiverContent: Yes, correct. You will get a call from the doctor's office, and if you don't receive any call after 11.30, you can call me back, and I can transfer you to them.

Seq8.ReceiverContent: Yeah, thank you for understanding, and sorry for the inconvenience, and take care of yourself.
